data.description: NEW PRICE!!!  Rare find in Sinton!!  This extra-large home on a huge corner lot has room for everyone! Spacious living room, an eat in kitchen and a dining room. All three bedrooms have their own bathroom.  Brand NEW carpet in all the bedrooms!!!  There's a half bath in the hall for guests. The back living area would make a great game room, playroom, office...or whatever you need it to be. Separate laundry room. There is another space that you could turn into an office or covert to another bedroom. The possibilities are endless.  This home is on .48 acres with lots of room in the backyard! There is a 2-car garage, plenty of parking and a carport. The storage building conveys!
